## ⚡ SenAI Agentic CRM Intelligence Platform
A production-grade, AI-powered Customer Relationship Management (CRM) system designed to autonomously triage high-volume inboxes, execute agentic workflows, and provide real-time market intelligence.

This repository represents a complete, end-to-end implementation of the SenAI Technical Assessment, passing all core requirements, advanced modules, special edge-case scenarios, and multiple bonus objectives.

## 🛠️ Tech Stack & Engineering Choices
# Frontend
React & Vite: Chosen for blazing-fast Hot Module Replacement (HMR) during development and highly optimized production builds.

Tailwind CSS: Utilized to build a premium, custom "Slate & Glass" design system without the bloat of heavy component libraries.

Recharts & Lucide React: Lightweight, SVG-based charting and iconography for the analytics dashboard and visual hierarchy.

# Backend
FastAPI (Python): The backbone of the API. Chosen for its native asynchronous support (critical for the background web scraper) and automatic OpenAPI/Swagger documentation.

Pydantic: Enforces strict data validation and schema sanitization (e.g., stripping malformed HTML and truncating 10,000+ character emails before they ever hit the database).

SQLAlchemy: Provides a secure, SQL-injection-resistant ORM layer while allowing raw SQL drop-ins for complex pgvector queries.

# AI & Intelligence
Google Gemini (2.5 Flash & Embeddings): Chosen for its massive context window and rapid inference speed.

Custom ReAct Engine: Instead of using LangChain's heavy abstraction, a native Reason + Act loop was built to ensure total deterministic control over circuit breakers and compliance rules.

# Database & Infrastructure
PostgreSQL (Supabase) + pgvector: Allows storing highly relational CRM data (threads, contacts, audit logs) alongside vector embeddings in a single, unified transaction layer.

Docker Compose: Containerizes the entire environment for a guaranteed "works on my machine" one-click deployment.

# 🚀 Quickstart & Setup Guide
1. Clone the Repository

git clone https://github.com/Omkar05-Tech/senai-crm-agent.git
cd senai-crm-agent

2. Environment Configuration
Create a .env file in the backend/ directory:

DATABASE_URL="postgresql://postgres.[YOUR_PROJECT]:[YOUR_PASSWORD]@aws-0-us-west-1.pooler.supabase.com:6543/postgres"
GEMINI_API_KEY="AIzaSyYourGeminiKeyHe....."

3. Docker Deployment (Bonus Objective Achieved)
Spin up the entire stack (FastAPI Backend + React/Vite Frontend) with a single command:

docker-compose up -d --build

4. Seed the Knowledge Base (RAG Pipeline)
Chunk the 6 required Markdown policies into 400-token overlapping segments and generate 768-dim embeddings in Supabase:

docker exec -it senai_backend python seed_rag.py

5. Run the Live Email Simulation
Stream the advanced dataset into the ingest endpoint (simulates real-time webhook traffic with idempotency):

python stream_simulator.py

